Plot: On their way to a gig, Sez and Matt's relationship is tested as they attempt to enhance their evening. When their plans don't meet their expectations, all of a sudden, just being together is no longer enough.
Title: Megan
Writer: Dane Dawson, Walter Lawry, Sarah Trass
Actors: Dane Dawson, Sarah Trass, Jordan Blaikie, Christina Cortesi
